      "status": "4",
      "last_action_date": "2013-04-23",
      "last_action": "Act 038, 4\/22\/2013 (Gov. Msg. No. 1138).",
      "title": "Public Land Development Corporation; Repeal",
      "description": "Repeals chapter 171C, HRS, relating to the PLDC. Transfers PLDC assets to the DLNR. Deposits funds appropriated to the DLNR pursuant to Act 55, SLH 2011, into the land conservation fund. Deposits proceeds in the stadium facilities special fund and the school facilities special fund into the general fund. (SD2)"
