      "last_action_date": "2013-01-22",
      "last_action": "Referred to JDL.",
      "title": "Criminal Procedure; Felonies; Information Charging",
      "description": "Authorizes all criminal charges for class B and C felonies to be instituted by written information unless the felony is expressly excluded. Effective July 1, 2013."
