      "last_action_date": "2013-03-07",
      "last_action": "Referred to HED, JUD, referral sheet 30",
      "title": "University of Hawaii; Board of Regents; General Counsel; Audit",
      "description": "Charges the Board of Regents with oversight of the University General Counsel. Exempts the Board of Regents, and repeals UH's exemption, from the prohibition to contract with attorneys. Requires the Auditor to review legal contracts entered into by UH. Effective 07\/01\/50. (SD2)"
